### Project Overview

- The PIP+ program will continue running for existing users but will not accept new signups
- The current Partners in Parenting website ([partnersparenting.com.au](http://partnersparenting.com.au)) will be converted into a hub/landing page that serves as an index to navigate users to different PIP program versions
- The [pipplus.web.app](http://pipplus.web.app) domain will remain unchanged for existing users
- This redesign will finally provide a central location listing all available PIP versions, addressing long-standing confusion about how many PIP programs exist

### Content Changes

- Remove all COVID-related content and imagery from the current website
- The new hub will list the following PIP versions:
    - PIP Teens (for parents of teenagers)
    - PIP Kids (for parents of primary school age children)
    - PIP KA (Kids with Autism)
    - PIP+ (existing program)
- Text content is provided in the shared document and should be followed strictly
- Minor text changes can be requested via comments in the document, with email escalation if no response
- Contact information has been updated to include new email

### Pages to Retain

- Keep Resources, About Us, and Contact Us pages
- Remove the sign-in button from the hub page - users will sign in through individual PIP program links
- Retain navigation tabs for subpages

### Design Requirements

- Create a completely new design that is modern but not outdated
- Keep the design simple and able to be completed quickly (estimated 2 days)
- Add subtle animations like sliding and dissolve effects, but avoid overly interactive elements
- The landing page will be a new, static application
- No need for complete new branding due to time constraints
- Clients are not expected to be highly particular about design details and have previously approved similar designs
- Use a simple template approach for subpages

### Technical Implementation

- The new hub will be a separate landing page with a new deployment
- Domain name will be changed to the new UI
- Design will be created using AI tools (possibly Lovable or similar) to expedite the process
- HTML files will be provided for development (Figma not required)

### Domain Name Context

- Multiple domain names currently exist for essentially identical deployments: [partnersparenting.com.au](http://partnersparenting.com.au) and [pipplus.web.app](http://pipplus.web.app)
- This is similar to other projects that maintain multiple domains for the same content
- Only the main [partnersparenting.com.au](http://partnersparenting.com.au) website will be modified in this project

### Timeline

- Design work: 2-3 days estimated
- Design delivery: Wednesday
- Initial review: Tuesday
- Final product delivery: End of next week (Friday)

